title: Ep - 50 -  Dorothy Wang of E! shows Rich Kids of Beverly Hills and Famously Single
description:
Dorothy Wang explains how she was cast for the E! shows Rich Kids of Beverly Hills and Famously Single, her childhood spent in China and Beverly Hills, and the impact of fame. Dallas makeup artist Becca Ashmon helps Kate review the season premiere of Life of Kylie and dissects the process and time it takes for Kylie to apply her face of makeup. Steve Gold from Million Dollar Listing New York talks about his real estate practice, joining the show, and dating in New York.
